# Plan Mode — Mandatory Pre-Plan Gate

**Every time you enter Plan mode or are asked to plan a feature, fix, or refactor, you MUST complete ALL steps below in order. Do NOT skip any step. Do NOT write any implementation code or call CreatePlan until the plan is approved by the user.**

For the full planning guide (all phases, TDD loop, finalization protocol, anti-patterns), read:

`/Users/alexguberman/Projects/chillist/chillist-docs/guides/planning.md`

---

