Read ALL of these files before doing anything else. If any file is missing, STOP and tell the user.

1. `/Users/alexguberman/Projects/chillist/chillist-docs/rules/common.md`
2. `/Users/alexguberman/Projects/chillist/chillist-docs/rules/backend.md`
